{"tid":1320501,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[我冇嘢講]聽我講，永遠要為對手留缺口","createTime":"2019-07-15T11:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T12:04:21.000Z","uid":280746,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"503e3679325b406d54e8a76da47abea83ea7c156","tid":1320501,"uid":280746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:53:26.000Z","msg":"我講打機策略，AOC<br />\n當處於優勢嘅時候，唔可以包圍死對手<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我直接講例子，上次包圍對手總部，<br />\n唔留缺口比員工放工，結果輿論輸咗</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">留缺口嘅好處係</span>，防止敵人作出必死嘅反抗<br />\n減低反抗力度<br />\n<br />\n尋日沙田新城市廣場就係包圍死示威者，<br />\n示威者要生存，作出本能嘅必死反抗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">心理上嘅應用係</span>，<br />\n要向軟化嘅前線招安，分化對手高層<br />\n<br />\n認同請分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9736b2f9c4230237ae4358ac6828798362dc7dcf","tid":1320501,"uid":280746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:53:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d796fd7ad27633c59c08a00bce80f638cffdc9de","tid":1320501,"uid":280746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:54:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee12ed9389bdace72046bf63f628053a292a149d","tid":1320501,"uid":280746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:54:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148e7779713257bdd277209d33eb030507b18f82","tid":1320501,"uid":280746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:55:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7e15d2e34f317bc4308cbccce5d95b2740af0b5","tid":1320501,"uid":280746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgm